The paper deals with computer vision techniques for estimating hand grip force, which is a problem related to robotics, human-computer interaction, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions robot teaching, haptic force feedback, and human-performed operations, which are related to robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and optical flow (cs.MM) for estimating grip force. Finally, the paper mentions the potential applications of the proposed method for human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
